### ============================================
### LOCAL TESTS (localhost)
### ============================================

### Get all contacts (Local)
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts

### Get single contact by id (Local) - John
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts/6a088e82fc65f561beda2ed0

### Create new contact (Local)
POST http://localhost:3000/contacts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "Local",
  "email": "[email protected]",
  "favoriteColor": "orange",
  "birthday": "2000-01-01"
}

### Update contact (Local) - REPLACE ID with one created above
PUT http://localhost:3000/contacts/REPLACE_WITH_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Updated",
  "lastName": "Local",
  "email": "[email protected]",
  "favoriteColor": "pink",
  "birthday": "2000-01-01"
}

### Delete contact (Local) - REPLACE ID
DELETE http://localhost:3000/contacts/REPLACE_WITH_ID


